        <hr>
        <p>Honey is a sweet substance made by bees from the nectar of flowers. Composed of more than 80% carbohydrates, it is a food rich in energy and relatively pure</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="single-service">
      <%= image_tag("6.jpg", :alt => "img") %>
      <!-- <img src="/assets/6.jpg" alt=""> -->
      <div class="overlay"></div>
      <div class="service-desc">
        <h3>Coconut oil</h3>
        <hr>
        <p>Moisturizing, soothing, antioxidant ... coconut oil is full of benefits. It can be used without moderation on the skin, on the hair, and can replace many beauty products.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="single-service">
      <%= image_tag("3.jpg", :alt => "img") %>
      <!-- <img src="/assets/3.jpg" alt=""> -->
      <div class="overlay"></div>
      <div class="service-desc">
        <h3>Palm oil</h3>
        <hr>
        <p>Emollient, nourishing and protective, palm oil is particularly moisturizing, and it is for this reason that it is widely used in soap.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="single-service">
      <%= image_tag("5.jpg", :alt => "img") %>
      <!-- <img src="/assets/5.jpg" alt=""> -->
      <div class="overlay"></div>
      <div class="service-desc">
        <h3>Sodabi liquor</h3>
        <hr>
        <p>Sodabi is a type of liquor made from distilled palm wine. Sodabi is more popular in the southern part of the country but can be found in northern markets as well.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

